<LocalizedProperties><Language>en</Language><Title>Security Update for Windows Server 2008 R2 x64 Edition (KB2984972)</Title><Description>A security issue has been identified in a Microsoft software product that could affect your system. You can help protect your system by installing this update from Microsoft. For a complete listing of the issues that are included in this update, see the associated Microsoft Knowledge Base article. After you install this update, you may have to restart your system.</Description><UninstallNotes>This software update can be removed by selecting View installed updates in the Programs and Features Control Panel.</UninstallNotes><MoreInfoUrl>http://support.microsoft.com/kb/2984972</MoreInfoUrl><SupportUrl>http://support.microsoft.com</SupportUrl></LocalizedProperties>